# noria:operationPlanPreCondition (used)
# noria:operationPlanPostCondition (used)
# noria:locatedAtLocus (used)
# noria:resourceManagementIPAddress (used)
# noria:clusterController (used)
# noria:productManufacturedBy (used)
# noria:networkInterfaceOf (used)
# noria:networkInterfaceConnects (used)
# noria:networkLinkTerminationResource (used)
# noria:networkLinkTerminationResourceOrigin (used)
# noria:networkLinkTerminationResourceDestination (used)

# Ensure all nodes are linked to at least one other node.
# All created entities have at least one property, and many are object properties.
# For example, noria:CorporateUserIdentifier is linked via foaf:holdsAccount.
# noria:Application is linked via noria:elementManagedBy.
# noria:ApplicationModule is linked via noria:applicationModuleOf.
# noria:Service is linked via noria:elementManagedBy.
# noria:TroubleTicket is linked via noria:troubleTicketRelatedService, noria:troubleTicketRelatedResource, noria:troubleTicketRelatedParty, noria:troubleTicketTrigger.
# noria:TroubleTicketNote is linked via dcterms:isPartOf.
# noria:ChangeRequest is linked via noria:changeRequestImpact, noria:changeRequestInitiatorParty, etc.
# noria:DocumentAttachment is linked via dcterms:isPartOf.
# noria:AnomalyPattern has folio:hasCause (datatype property, but it's a subclass of folio:FailureMode which might have object properties).
# noria:OperationPlan has noria:operationPlanPreCondition, noria:operationPlanPostCondition.
# noria:ActionPreCondition and noria:ActionPostCondition are linked by OperationPlan.
# noria:Room has bot:hasSpace.
# noria:Locus is linked by noria:locatedAtLocus.
# noria:EventRecord is linked by noria:logOriginatingManagedObject, noria:logOriginatingManagementSystem, noria:logOriginatingAgent.
# noria:Resource is linked by noria:resourceProductModel, noria:resourceForApplication, noria:locatedAtLocus, noria:resourceManagedBy.
# noria:NetworkInterface is linked by noria:networkInterfaceOf, noria:networkInterfaceConnects.
# noria:NetworkLink is linked by noria:networkLinkTerminationResource, noria:networkLinkTerminationResourceOrigin, noria:networkLinkTerminationResourceDestination.
# noria:ProductModel is linked by noria:productManufacturedBy.

# The graph is quite extensive with multiple instances for each class and various interconnections.
